---
import Article from '../layouts/Article.astro';
---

<Article
  title="[TOOL NAME] Review 2026: [COMPELLING SUBTITLE UNDER 60 CHARS TOTAL]"
  description="[150-160 CHAR DESCRIPTION. Include primary keyword naturally. First person operator perspective.]"
  publishDate="[YYYY-MM-DD]"
  category="[CATEGORY] Review"
  readTime="[X] min read"
>

<!-- ─── VERDICT BOX ─── -->
<div class="verdict-box">
  <div class="verdict-stars">
    <span class="star">&#9733;</span>
    <span class="star">&#9733;</span>
    <span class="star">&#9733;</span>
    <span class="star">&#9733;</span>
    <span class="star empty">&#9733;</span>
  </div>
  <h3>Verdict: [X.X] / 5 — [ONE-LINE POSITIONING STATEMENT]</h3>
  <p>[2-3 SENTENCE SUMMARY. What the tool does, who it's best for, and the single biggest caveat. Be direct.]</p>
</div>

<!-- ─── QUICK STATS ─── -->
<div class="quick-stats">
  <div class="quick-stat"><span class="stat-number">[X.X/5]</span><span class="stat-label">Rating</span></div>
  <div class="quick-stat"><span class="stat-number">$[XX]</span><span class="stat-label">Per month</span></div>
  <div class="quick-stat"><span class="stat-number">[KEY METRIC]</span><span class="stat-label">[METRIC LABEL]</span></div>
  <div class="quick-stat"><span class="stat-number">[XX%]</span><span class="stat-label">Affiliate commission</span></div>
</div>

<!-- ─── TABLE OF CONTENTS ─── -->
<!-- NOTE: TOC is auto-generated by the sidebar component from h2/h3 headings.
     Just make sure every h2 and h3 has an id attribute. -->

<!-- ─── WHAT IS [TOOL] ─── -->
<h2 id="what-is">&#128270; What Is [TOOL NAME]?</h2>

<p>[WHAT THE TOOL DOES IN 1-2 SENTENCES. Category, primary function, who built it.]</p>

<p>[HOW IT FITS IN THE OPERATOR STACK. What it replaces. Why it matters for multi-location businesses specifically.]</p>

<!-- ─── MY EXPERIENCE ─── -->
<h2 id="my-experience">&#128100; My Experience</h2>

<p>[HOW I DISCOVERED/STARTED USING THIS TOOL. Reference our team, thousands of venues. What I was using before.]</p>

<p>[SPECIFIC DEPLOYMENT DETAILS. How many venues use it. How long I've been on it. What changed after switching.]</p>

<p>[THE MOMENT IT CLICKED OR THE MOMENT I SAW THE PROBLEM. A specific anecdote that shows real usage.]</p>

<div class="callout callout-blue">
  <strong>[TIP HEADING]</strong>
  [PRACTICAL TIP FROM REAL EXPERIENCE. Something most review sites wouldn't know.]
</div>

<!-- ─── FEATURE BREAKDOWN ─── -->
<h2 id="features">&#9881;&#65039; Key Features Reviewed</h2>

<h3 id="feature-1">[FEATURE 1 NAME]</h3>

<p>[WHAT THIS FEATURE DOES. 2-3 sentences.]</p>

<p>[HOW I USE IT IN PRACTICE. Specific workflow or example from our team deployment.]</p>

<h3 id="feature-2">[FEATURE 2 NAME]</h3>

<p>[WHAT THIS FEATURE DOES.]</p>

<p>[REAL-WORLD ASSESSMENT. Be honest -- does it actually work well?]</p>

<h3 id="feature-3">[FEATURE 3 NAME]</h3>

<p>[WHAT THIS FEATURE DOES.]</p>

<p>[HONEST TAKE. Include cons here if relevant.]</p>

<!-- MID-ARTICLE CTA -->
<a href="https://operatorstack.tech/recommends/[TOOLNAME]" class="affiliate-cta">
  [SPECIFIC CTA TEXT -- e.g., "Start Your Free 30-Day Trial"] &rarr;
</a>

<div class="callout callout-orange">
  <strong>[WARNING HEADING]</strong>
  [HONEST WARNING OR CAVEAT. Something a user should know before signing up.]
</div>

<!-- ─── PRICING ─── -->
<h2 id="pricing">&#128176; Pricing</h2>

<table>
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>Plan</th>
      <th>Price</th>
      <th>Key Features</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td>[FREE/STARTER PLAN]</td>
      <td>$[X]/mo</td>
      <td>[WHAT'S INCLUDED]</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><strong>[RECOMMENDED PLAN]</strong></td>
      <td><strong>$[X]/mo</strong></td>
      <td><strong>[WHAT'S INCLUDED -- BOLD THE RECOMMENDED TIER]</strong></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>[TOP PLAN]</td>
      <td>$[X]/mo</td>
      <td>[WHAT'S INCLUDED]</td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<p><strong>My recommendation:</strong> [WHICH PLAN AND WHY. Reference operator scale -- "for operators with X+ locations, the Y plan is the right call."]</p>

<!-- ─── PROS & CONS ─── -->
<h2 id="pros-cons">&#9989; Pros &amp; Cons</h2>

<div class="pros-cons">
  <div class="pros">
    <h4>Pros</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>[PRO 1 -- most important first]</li>
      <li>[PRO 2]</li>
      <li>[PRO 3]</li>
      <li>[PRO 4]</li>
      <li>[PRO 5]</li>
      <li>[PRO 6]</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="cons">
    <h4>Cons</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>[CON 1 -- be genuinely honest]</li>
      <li>[CON 2]</li>
      <li>[CON 3]</li>
      <li>[CON 4]</li>
      <li>[CON 5]</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ─── WHO IT'S FOR ─── -->
<h2 id="who-its-for">&#127919; Who It's For</h2>

<p><strong>[TOOL NAME] is right for you if:</strong></p>
<ul>
  <li>[CRITERIA 1 -- be specific about operator type/scale]</li>
  <li>[CRITERIA 2]</li>
  <li>[CRITERIA 3]</li>
  <li>[CRITERIA 4]</li>
  <li>[CRITERIA 5]</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Skip [TOOL NAME] if:</strong></p>
<ul>
  <li>[SKIP CRITERIA 1 -- suggest alternative]</li>
  <li>[SKIP CRITERIA 2]</li>
  <li>[SKIP CRITERIA 3]</li>
  <li>[SKIP CRITERIA 4]</li>
</ul>

<!-- ─── FINAL VERDICT ─── -->
<h2 id="verdict">&#127942; Final Verdict</h2>

<div class="verdict-box">
  <div class="verdict-stars">
    <span class="star">&#9733;</span>
    <span class="star">&#9733;</span>
    <span class="star">&#9733;</span>
    <span class="star">&#9733;</span>
    <span class="star empty">&#9733;</span>
  </div>
  <h3>[X.X] / 5 — [SHORT VERDICT TITLE]</h3>
  <p>[FINAL 2-3 SENTENCE ASSESSMENT. Summarize who should buy it and why. End with a clear recommendation, not a hedge.]</p>
</div>

<!-- END CTA -->
<a href="https://operatorstack.tech/recommends/[TOOLNAME]" class="affiliate-cta" style="margin-top:2rem;">
  [SPECIFIC CTA TEXT] &rarr;
</a>

<!-- ─── FURTHER READING ─── -->
<div class="callout callout-green" style="margin-top:2.5rem;">
  <strong>Further Reading</strong>
  <ul style="margin:0.5rem 0 0; padding-left:1.25rem;">
    <li><a href="/[RELATED-ARTICLE-1]">[RELATED ARTICLE 1 TITLE]</a></li>
    <li><a href="/[RELATED-ARTICLE-2]">[RELATED ARTICLE 2 TITLE]</a></li>
    <li><a href="/[RELATED-ARTICLE-3]">[RELATED ARTICLE 3 TITLE]</a></li>
  </ul>
</div>

<!--
  PUBLISHING CHECKLIST (delete this block before publishing):
  - [ ] npm run build passes, zero errors
  - [ ] Added to src/pages/blog/index.astro
  - [ ] Added to src/pages/reviews/index.astro
  - [ ] Added to src/pages/rss.xml.js
  - [ ] publishDate set to today
  - [ ] All placeholder [BRACKETS] replaced
  - [ ] All internal links point to real pages
  - [ ] Affiliate link URL is correct
  - [ ] At least 3 internal links in body content
-->

</Article>
